        <p>Mason County, Kentucky, wool carder. Kentucky native. Married to Hannah J. Knight. Father of Sarah H. Knight, Malissa Knight, William A. Knight, Cordelia Knight, Alfred P. Knight, Rebecca Knight. Married to Judy Knight. Father of Lizzie Knight. Wool carder in Mason County in 1860. </p>

